✓ Use freely — personal projects, research, local model conversion
✓ Share and fork — allowed, under the same terms
✓ Credit required — derivatives must acknowledge Tsunagi and link to the original repo
✗ No commercial use — can't be used in paid tools, hosted services, or API backends
⚠ Models need a notice — anything built with Tsunagi must disclose it in the model card

